Storyline:

Tom Selleck and Sam Elliot star as brothers who battled on opposing sides of the Civil War. When they return home, they discover that their family, including a younger brother and one of the brother's fiancee, have been kidnapped by a marauding band of rebel guerrillas who refuse to accept the defeat of the Confederacy. The women are destined to be sold to a foreign whorehouse . Aided by their uncle, they set out to rescue the family.
